OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FSurvivors of the Nottingham attacks
OL,8,Fhave told an official inquiry that
OL,9,Fpolice failures caused "extra
OL,10,Fsuffering" for victims' families.
OL,12,FWayne Birkett, left with severe brain
OL,13,Finjuries after being deliberately run
OL,14,Fover by Valdo Calocane, and his
OL,15,Fpartner Tracey Hodgson accused
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police of withholding
OL,17,Fcritical information, leaving families
OL,18,Fin prolonged anguish.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FTracey told the Nottingham attack
OL,8,Finquiry: "It should not have needed
OL,9,Fthis inquiry for the police in
OL,10,Fparticular to tell the truth and be
OL,11,Fhonest.
OL,13,F"All organisations should have been
OL,14,Fopen from the beginning and they have
OL,15,Fcaused extra suffering for the
OL,16,Ffamilies.
OL,18,F"They should have been allowed to just
OL,19,Fget on with grieving, you have
OL,20,Ftortured theses families over and over
OL,21,Fagain."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
