OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FMr Birkett was thrown into the air
OL,8,Fwhen Calocane deliberately swerved and
OL,9,Fhit him with a stolen van that he was
OL,10,Fdriving in the early hours of 13 June
OL,11,F2023 in Nottingham.
OL,13,FMr Birkett's attacker had already
OL,14,Fkilled three people that morning `
OL,15,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,16,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and school
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, whose van he
OL,18,Fused to run over three people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FGiving evidence to the Nottingham
OL,8,FInquiry, which is examining events
OL,9,Fleading up to and after the attacks,
OL,10,FMr Birkett and his partner Tracey
OL,11,FHodgson said the survivors of the
OL,12,Fattacks feel "forgotten".
OL,14,FMr Birkett said he wanted to know the
OL,15,F"severity" of what Calocane did, but
OL,16,Ftold the inquiry that their family
OL,17,Fliaison officer, Detective Constable
OL,18,FRaj Johal, in an early meeting, did
OL,19,Fnot tell them about the killer's
OL,20,Fprevious interactions with the police.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@XO]wD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FMs Hodgson said: "She said there was
OL,8,Fno history at all with the police.
OL,10,F"She's been sitting on all this
OL,11,Finformation that she already knew.
OL,13,F"It's so disappointing to know that
OL,14,Fshe would have known all of this and
OL,15,Fshe wasn't allowed to tell us,
OL,16,Fobviously."
OL,18,FMr Birkett suffered a traumatic brain
OL,19,Finjury as a result of two skull
OL,20,Ffractures, numerous lacerations,
OL,21,Fsevere bruising and multiple fractures.
OL,26,@oD@ROUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
