PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FThe inquiry previously heard that
OL,8,FCalocane assaulted and stalked a
OL,9,Fformer flatmate, and had attacked two
OL,10,Fmembers of staff at a warehouse a
OL,11,Fmonth before the Nottingham attacks.
OL,13,FA warrant was issued for his arrest
OL,14,Fafter he failed to attend court in
OL,15,FSeptember 2022, for assaulting a
OL,16,Fpolice officer on a separate occasion.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
