PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FMr Birkett said of the sentencing
OL,8,Fhearing for Calocane: "I thought it
OL,9,Fwas horrifying listening to what
OL,10,Fhappened because I wasn't expecting it
OL,11,Fat all.
OL,13,F"I had to literally walk past VC
OL,14,F(Valdo Calocane), probably within two
OL,15,Fmetres of him, every time I had to
OL,16,Fleave the court.
OL,18,F"How do you do that, staring at the
OL,19,Fman who did all this?"
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOUzD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FMs Hodgson said it was "not the right
OL,8,Fsentence".
OL,10,FCalocane was handed an indefinite
OL,11,Fhospital order in January 2024 after
OL,12,Fadmitting three counts of manslaughter
OL,13,Fand three counts of attempted murder.
OL,15,FGiving evidence to the inquiry, fellow
OL,16,Fsurvivor Sharon Miller said she
OL,17,Fthought she was a "goner" after being
OL,18,Fhit by a stolen van driven by
OL,19,FCalocane, and she believed the killer
OL,20,Fhad been "spooked" by police who were
OL,21,Ffollowing him.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@IO]yD@SOUyD@YO]|D@JOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FShe said: "When the police car was
OL,8,Fbehind the van, VC was letting people
OL,9,Fcross the road.
OL,11,F"As soon as the sirens went on it must
OL,12,Fhave spooked him and that's when he
OL,13,Fcame after me."
OL,15,FShe recalled how she had got off the
OL,16,Fbus at King Street and was about to
OL,17,Fcross the road when she saw the police
OL,18,Fcar with its lights on behind the van
OL,19,Fbefore she was hit.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FShe said: "I assumed police were
OL,8,Fpulling them over. Next minute I'm up
OL,9,Fin the air and the ambulance came."
OL,11,FShe added: "A lady from the train
OL,12,Fstation and the police that were
OL,13,Fdriving the police car helped me.
OL,15,F"I told them to help Marcin
OL,16,F(Gawronski, who was also hit) and he
OL,17,Flooked like he was going to pass
OL,18,Fout... he
OL,20,Flooked like he was going to fall on
OL,21,Fthe floor."
OL,26,@oD@KOUqD@cO]sD@LOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FSpeaking to counsel to the inquiry
OL,8,FRachel Langdale KC, Ms Miller said she
OL,9,Fwas "absolutely disgusted" to learn
OL,10,Fvia the media that police had had
OL,11,Fprevious dealings with Calocane and
OL,12,Fthat there had been a warrant out for
OL,13,Fhis arrest before the attacks.
OL,15,FMs Miller also questioned why Calocane
OL,16,Fwas allowed to "roam the streets" for
OL,17,Fso long after the attacks.
OL,19,FShe said: "I think it's disgusting how
OL,20,Flong it took them to get him on the
OL,21,Fmorning (of the attacks).
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@ZO]xD@POUxD@aO]{D@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,F"There's that much CCTV where we were
OL,8,Fwalking. Why did it take so long to
OL,9,Fget him?"
OL,11,FAsked how she felt after being
OL,12,Finformed Calocane had pleaded guilty
OL,13,Fto three counts of attempted murder in
OL,14,Frelation to those he had hit with the
OL,15,Fvan, Ms Miller said: "Not very good,
OL,16,Fit just put me on another downer, that
OL,17,Fhe could even say he wanted to kill
OL,18,Fme."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]wD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774645562
OL,3,CSurvivor tells Nottingham attack
OL,4,Cinquiry police 'tortured these
OL,5,Cfamilies'
OL,7,FAsked if she felt "sidelined" as
OL,8,Fvictims who survived, Ms Miller said:
OL,9,F"Definitely."
OL,11,FShe added: "I felt like I had come out
OL,12,Fof hospital and was pushed aside."
OL,14,FMs Miller said the way the situation
OL,15,Fhas been dealt with has led to her
OL,16,Flosing faith in the police.
OL,18,FShe told the inquiry: "All they keep
OL,19,Fdoing is blaming each other for their
OL,20,Fmistakes."
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@]O]qD@AOUqD@MO]sD@LOUtD@bO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU|D@JO]
